'''杰森·斯科特·马奎斯'''（{{lang-en|Jason Scott Marquis}}，{{bd|1978年|8月21日|||Marquis, Jason}}）出生于[[美国|美国]][[纽约州|纽约州]][[曼哈塞特_(纽约州)|曼哈塞特]]，是美国职棒[[投手|投手]]，目前是[[自由球員|自由球員]]。他曾效力于[[亚特兰大勇士|亚特兰大勇士]]、[[圣路易红雀|圣路易红雀]]、[[芝加哥小熊|芝加哥小熊]]、[[科罗拉多落矶|科罗拉多落矶]]、[[華盛頓國民|華盛頓國民]]、[[亞利桑那響尾蛇|亞利桑那響尾蛇]]、[[聖地牙哥教士|聖地牙哥教士]]、[[明尼蘇達雙城|明尼蘇達雙城]]及[[辛辛那提紅人|辛辛那提紅人]]。

马奎斯12岁时曾在[[世界少棒大赛|少年棒球联盟世界大赛]]投出过[[无安打比赛|无安打比赛]]，并和球队一起获得第三名。他也是少数参加过世界少棒大赛和大联盟[[世界大赛|世界大赛]]的球员<ref name = "Almanac">{{cite web | url = http://www.baseball-almanac.com/players/player.php?p=marquja01 | title = Jason Marquis Stats | publisher = Baseball Almanac | accessdate = 2009-07-20 | archive-date = 2021-01-26 | archive-url = https://web.archive.org/web/20210126144319/https://www.baseball-almanac.com/players/player.php?p=marquja01 | dead-url = no }}</ref>。高中时期他和球队连续获得纽约州的冠军。高中毕业後被当时的世界大赛冠军[[亚特兰大勇士|亚特兰大勇士]]在第一轮选中，{{MLBy|2000年}}马奎斯以21岁的年纪首次登上大联盟。

从{{MLBy|2004年}}起马奎斯连续六个赛季先发28场以上，并拿到11胜以上的成绩。他在{{MLBy|2004年}}至{{MLBy|2008年}}期间拿到的65胜在国联投手中排名第七<ref>{{cite web | url = http://colorado.rockies.mlb.com/news/press_releases/press_release.jsp?ymd=20090106&content_id=3734415&vkey=pr_col&fext=.jsp&c_id=col | title = Rockies acquire RHP Jason Marquis from Cubs; Right-handed reliever Luis Vizcaino sent to Chicago in deal | publisher = [[MLB.com|MLB.com]] | date = 2009-01-06 | accessdate = 2009-07-20 | deadurl = yes | archiveurl = https://web.archive.org/web/20120310084320/http://colorado.rockies.mlb.com/news/press_releases/press_release.jsp?ymd=20090106&content_id=3734415&vkey=pr_col&fext=.jsp&c_id=col | archivedate = 2012年3月10日 | df =  }}</ref>。作为一名投手，马奎斯的打击出色，生涯迄今为止一共击出过5支全垒打，并在{{MLBy|2005年}}获得过国联投手[[美国职棒大联盟银棒奖|银棒奖]]。

== 早年生活 ==
马奎斯出生于[[纽约州|纽约州]]的[[曼哈塞特_(纽约州)|曼哈塞特]]，并在[[史泰登岛|史泰登岛]]度过童年生活<ref name="Almanac" />。他的母亲在纽约市教育委员会工作，拥有教育学位，他的父亲则在[[布鲁克林区|布鲁克林区]]拥有一个支票兑现业务<ref name=CT>{{cite news|last=Rosenbloom|first=Steve|title=Out loud with Jason Marquis: Cubs pitcher tells Our Guy about his role models, growing up in New York, and his bar mitzvah|publisher=''芝加哥论坛报''|url=http://www.chicagotribune.com/sports/cs-070924outloudmarquis,0,6714694.story|date=September 24, 2007|accessdate=May 27, 2009|archive-date=2014-03-09|archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20140309183948/http://www.chicagotribune.com/sports/cs-070924outloudmarquis,0,6714694.story|dead-url=no}}</ref>。马奎斯是[[犹太人|犹太人]]，成长在一个保守派犹太教家庭，就读希伯来语学校，并庆祝犹太节日<ref>{{cite web | url = http://reds.enquirer.com/2004/08/30/red2a.html | last = Muder | first = Craig | title = Hall of Fame celebrates Jewish Players | publisher = ''辛辛那提提讯报'' | date = 2004-08-30 | accessdate = 2007-06-06 | archive-url = https://web.archive.org/web/20070930131934/http://reds.enquirer.com/2004/08/30/red2a.html | archive-date = 2007-09-30 | dead-url = yes }}</ref><ref name=CJN>{{cite news|last=Shupak|first=Eli|title=Cubs pitcher plays his best in day games|publisher=''加拿大犹太新闻报''|url=http://www.cjnews.com/index.php?option=com_content&task=view&id=14934&Itemid=73|date=June 25, 2008|accessdate=May 27, 2009|archive-date=2015-09-23|archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20150923205532/http://www.cjnews.com/index.php?option=com_content&task=view&id=14934&Itemid=73|dead-url=no}}</ref><ref name=CJN2>{{cite news|last=Rosen|first=Harvey|title=Baseball rosters dotted with players of the Jewish persuasion|publisher=''加拿大犹太新闻报''|url=http://www.cjnews.com/index2.php?option=com_content&task=view&id=3245&pop=1&page=0&Itemid=86|date=4/10/03|accessdate=May 27, 2009|deadurl=yes|archiveurl=https://web.archive.org/web/20110606160549/http://www.cjnews.com/index2.php?option=com_content&task=view&id=3245&pop=1&page=0&Itemid=86|archivedate=2011年6月6日}}</ref>。“我的母亲严格按照犹太习俗来培养我们，”马奎斯说，“她的父母都是纳粹大屠杀的幸存者。”马奎斯是{{MLBy|2008年}}汉克·格林伯格75周年纪念版本的大联盟犹太球员卡片的人物之一，此卡片是为了纪念从{{MLBy|1871年}}以来曾进入过大联盟的犹太球员<ref>{{cite web | url = http://www.metrowestdailynews.com/news/x1192322494/Shedding-light-on-baseballs-Jewish-history | last = Uek | first = Kathy | title = Shedding light on baseball's Jewish history | publisher = ''MetroWest每日新闻报'' | date = 2008-05-19 | accessdate = 2008-06-16 | archive-date = 2011-06-14 | archive-url = https://web.archive.org/web/20110614003624/http://www.metrowestdailynews.com/news/x1192322494/Shedding-light-on-baseballs-Jewish-history | dead-url = yes }}</ref>。卡片包括的球员还有[[布拉德·奥斯默斯|布拉德·奥斯默斯]]（[[:en:Brad_Ausmus|Brad Ausmus]]）、[[凯文·尤克里斯|凯文·尤克里斯]]、[[伊安·金斯勒|伊安·金斯勒]]、[[莱恩·布劳恩|莱恩·布劳恩]]、[[盖比·凯普勒|盖比·凯普勒]]（[[:en:Gabe_Kapler|Gabe Kapler]]）、[[斯科特·费尔曼|斯科特·费尔曼]]（[[:en:Scott_Feldman|Scott Feldman]]）、[[杰森·赫什|杰森·赫什]]（[[:en:Jason_Hirsh|Jason Hirsh]]）、[[约翰·格拉博|约翰·格拉博]]（[[:en:John_Grabow|John Grabow]]）、[[克雷格·布雷斯洛|克雷格·布雷斯洛]]、[[斯科特·舒恩维斯|斯科特·舒恩维斯]]（[[:en:Scott_Schoeneweis|Scott Schoeneweis]]）<ref>{{cite web | url = http://mlb.mlb.com/news/article.jsp?ymd=20040830&content_id=842659&vkey=news_mlb&fext=.jsp&c_id=null | last = Francis | first = Bill | title = Jewish players celebrated at Hall | publisher = ''[[MLB.com|MLB.com]]'' | date = 2004-08-30 | accessdate = 2009-08-21 | archive-date = 2013-12-12 | archive-url = https://web.archive.org/web/20131212063321/http://mlb.mlb.com/news/article.jsp?ymd=20040830&content_id=842659&vkey=news_mlb&fext=.jsp&c_id=null | dead-url = no }}</ref>。马奎斯小时候是[[纽约洋基|纽约洋基]]的球迷，最崇拜的偶像是[[唐·马丁利|唐·马丁利]]（[[:en:Don_Mattingly|Don Mattingly]]）<ref name=CT/>。从小和他关系最好的叔叔史蒂夫·贝克是他的启蒙教练，曾教他如何投球。

=== 世界少棒大赛 ===
马奎斯曾是南岸少棒队的明星球员，他在[[少年棒球联盟|少年棒球联盟]]表现出色，1991年时率队获得全美第二名，并在[[世界少棒大赛|世界少棒大赛]]取得第三名<ref name=CT/><ref>{{cite web | url = http://sports.espn.go.com/espn/wire?section=mlb&id=1907492 | title = World Series may pit former Little League stars against each other | publisher = ''[[ESPN|ESPN]]'' | date = 2004-10-25 | accessdate = 2007-06-06 | archive-date = 2016-01-06 | archive-url = https://web.archive.org/web/20160106121405/http://sports.espn.go.com/espn/wire?section=mlb&id=1907492 | dead-url = no }}</ref>。

南岸队在第一轮击败了[[查德·潘宁顿|查德·潘宁顿]]所在的俄亥俄队，马奎斯投出了三安打完封胜，自己还击出三支安打和三分打点<ref>{{cite web | url = http://www.nytimes.com/1991/08/22/sports/little-league-world-series-a-team-new-yorkers-can-be-proud-of.html | title = Little League World Series: A Team New Yorkers Can Be Proud Of | publisher = ''[[纽约时报|纽约时报]]'' | date = 1991-08-22 | accessdate = 2009-08-19 | archive-date = 2016-03-04 | archive-url = https://web.archive.org/web/20160304203902/http://www.nytimes.com/1991/08/22/sports/little-league-world-series-a-team-new-yorkers-can-be-proud-of.html | dead-url = no }}</ref>。他们在决赛中输给了加州队，该场比赛马奎斯打的是[[游击手|游击手]]的位置，因为少棒联盟不允许一名球员连两天上场投球<ref>{{cite web | url = http://www.nytimes.com/1991/08/23/sports/baseball-there-is-no-joy-in-staten-island.html | title = Baseball:  There Is No Joy In Staten Island | publisher = ''[[纽约时报|纽约时报]]'' | date = 1991-08-23 | accessdate = 2009-08-19 | archive-date = 2016-03-04 | archive-url = https://web.archive.org/web/20160304064022/http://www.nytimes.com/1991/08/23/sports/baseball-there-is-no-joy-in-staten-island.html | dead-url = no }}</ref>。随后马奎斯在世界少棒大赛第三名的争夺战中投出了[[无安打比赛|无安打比赛]]<ref name=CT/>。“那时在那么多人面前比赛的情景让我明白了我此生应该做些什么，”马奎斯说，“我要尽我最大的努力去实现。”<ref name=CT/> 截止至2008年，共有31名参加过[[世界少棒大赛|世界少棒大赛]]的球员进入大联盟，马奎斯是其中之一<ref>{{cite web | url = http://www.littleleague.org/media/newsarchive/2008stories/PlayoffExperience_LLAlumsinMLB.htm | title = Playoff Experience: Quartet of Little League World Series Alums Playing in 2008 MLB Postseason | publisher = ''少棒联盟在线'' | date = 2008-10-02 | accessdate = 2009-08-20 | deadurl = yes | archiveurl = https://web.archive.org/web/20110607000922/http://www.littleleague.org/media/newsarchive/2008stories/PlayoffExperience_LLAlumsinMLB.htm | archivedate = 2011-06-07 }}</ref>。

在马奎斯的成人礼上，他父母的礼物给了他一个惊喜——一个复制的20英尺宽、15英尺高的记分板，上面记录了当年他在世界少棒大赛对加拿大投出无安打比赛的成绩<ref name=CT/>。

=== 高中时期 ===
“高一时我的身高只有5英尺2英寸，所有人都认为我太矮了，”马奎斯说，“但我总是梦想着能进入大联盟，所以我一直很努力。”<ref name=POY>{{cite web|last=Brennan|first=Sean|title= Player of the Year |publisher= ''[[纽约每日新闻报|纽约每日新闻报]]'' |url=http://www.nydailynews.com/archives/news/1996/06/24/1996-06-24_player_of_the_year.html |date=1996-06-24  |accessdate=July 20, 2009 }}</ref> 到了高四时马奎斯长高到了6英尺1英寸，并且他投出的93英里[[快速球|快速球]]和[[曲球|曲球]]在高中等级几乎达到无敌的程度<ref>{{cite web | url = http://www.nydailynews.com/archives/sports/1996/05/05/1996-05-05_a_marquis_attraction__totten.html | last = Rubin | first = Roger | title = A Marquis Attraction:  Tottenville Pitcher a Top Prop Prospect | publisher = ''纽约每日新闻报'' | date = 1996-05-05 | accessdate = 2009-08-19}}</ref>。他率领的托滕维尔高中连续两年获得[[纽约市|纽约市]]公立校体育联盟（PSAL）的冠军。第一年决赛他们在[[谢亚球场|谢亚球场]]以3比2击败了乔治华盛顿特罗伊队，该赛季马奎斯投出惊人的11胜0败的成绩，在61局的投球中送出86次三振<ref name=POY/><ref>{{cite web | url = http://www.nydailynews.com/archives/sports/1995/06/07/1995-06-07_tottenville_s_town.html | last = James | first = Michael | title = Tottenville's Town | publisher = ''纽约每日新闻报'' | date = 1995-06-07 | accessdate = 2009-07-21}}</ref>。第二年他们再度在决赛中以5比1击败乔治华盛顿特罗伊队，这场在[[洋基体育场_(1923年)|洋基体育场]]进行的比赛中，马奎斯投了7局[[完全比赛|完全比赛]]，并有15次三振，他自己还击出了一支两分打点的三垒安打<ref>{{cite web | last = Glickson | first = Grant | url = http://select.nytimes.com/gst/abstract.html?res=F00D14FF3C5D0C728DDDAF0894DE494D81&n=Top%2fReference%2fTimes%20Topics%2fSubjects%2fI%2fInterscholastic%20Athletics | title = Marquis Pitches Tottenville To Its Second Straight Title | publisher = ''纽约时报'' | date = 1996-06-11 | accessdate = 2007-06-06}}</ref>。该赛季马奎斯投出14胜1败、防御率0.40、150次三振的成绩，作为打者他打击率达到4成68，还击出了11支全垒打，追平了学校单赛季纪录<ref name=POY/>。

马奎斯当年获得了象征PSAL最佳棒球球员的铁马奖，以及纽约每日新闻报评选的年度最佳球员奖，并入选全美高中第一队<ref name=POY/><ref>{{cite web | url = http://www.nydailynews.com/archives/sports/1998/05/12/1998-05-12_no_quit_in_ex-ram_hage.html | last = Brennan | first = Sean | title = No Quit in Ex-Ram Hage | publisher = ''纽约每日新闻报'' | date = 1998-05-12 | accessdate = 2009-08-19}}</ref><ref>{{cite web | url = http://www.thebaseballcube.com/Awards/M/Jason-Marquis.shtml | title = Jason Marquis:  Awards | publisher = ''The Baseball Cube'' | accessdate = 2009-07-20 | archive-date = 2010-07-27 | archive-url = https://web.archive.org/web/20100727152939/http://www.thebaseballcube.com/Awards/M/Jason-Marquis.shtml | dead-url = no }}</ref>。纽约每日新闻报的安东尼·麦卡伦认为他是“自[[曼尼·拉米瑞兹|曼尼·拉米瑞兹]]以来纽约市最优秀的棒球选手”，[[美国棒球|美国棒球]]杂志把他排在全国未来之星的第39位<ref>{{cite web | url = http://www.nydailynews.com/archives/news/1996/06/24/1996-06-24_tott_s_almost_all__folks.html | last = McCarron | first = Anthony | title = Tott's Almost All, Folks | publisher = ''纽约每日新闻报'' | date = 1996-06-24 | accessdate = 2009-08-19}}</ref><ref>{{cite web | url = http://www.nytimes.com/1996/06/04/sports/baseball-fishing-for-future-stars-in-the-draft.html | last = Smith | first = Claire | title = Baseball:  Fishing for Future Stars in the Draft | publisher = ''纽约时报'' | date = 1996-06-04 | accessdate = 2009-08-19 | archive-date = 2018-01-27 | archive-url = https://web.archive.org/web/20180127202337/http://www.nytimes.com/1996/06/04/sports/baseball-fishing-for-future-stars-in-the-draft.html | dead-url = no }}</ref>。高中时期他还曾打过篮球，在学习方面他是国家荣誉协会的成员<ref name=BB>{{cite web | last = Horvitz | first = Joachim | title = The Big Book of Jewish Baseball, p. 277 | publisher = SP Books | url = http://books.google.com/books?id=9ZzxydPInwgC&pg=PA277&lpg=PA277&dq=%22jason+marquis%22+%22danville%22&source=bl&ots=tOpS5UzMSP&sig=DU2gp3PO0fTT3zXlDitGxfoVzGU&hl=en&ei=5_cdSvnQFozKMvaVgPUF&sa=X&oi=book_result&ct=result&resnum=22 | date = 2001 | accessdate = May 27, 2009}}</ref><ref name=MLB>{{cite web |title=Jason Marquis Biography |publisher=''[[MLB.com|MLB.com]]'' |url=http://mlb.mlb.com/team/player.jsp?player_id=150302 |accessdate=May 27, 2009 |archive-date=2015-04-06 |archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20150406023524/http://mlb.mlb.com/team/player.jsp?player_id=150302 |dead-url=no }}</ref>。

效力于[[芝加哥熊|芝加哥熊]]的防守端锋[[艾德维尔·奥滚雷耶|艾德维尔·奥滚雷耶]]（[[:en:Adewale_Ogunleye|Adewale Ogunleye]]）是他的高中同学<ref>{{cite web | url = http://sports.espn.go.com/espnmag/story?id=3618254 | last = Bauer | first = Ted | title = Fun Facts:  Dodgers vs. Cubs | publisher = ''ESPN'' | accessdate = 2009-07-20 | archive-date = 2015-04-15 | archive-url = https://web.archive.org/web/20150415052315/http://sports.espn.go.com/espnmag/story?id=3618254 | dead-url = no }}</ref>。

马奎斯原本计划进入提供给他奖学金的[[邁阿密大學_(佛罗里达州)|邁阿密大學]]就读<ref name=POY/>。在[[1996年美国职棒大联盟选秀|1996年大联盟选秀]]当天，马奎斯正在参加高中季後赛，他的母亲在家中接到了他被世界大赛冠军[[亚特兰大勇士|亚特兰大勇士]]在第一轮35顺位选中的电话<ref name=CT/>。马奎斯十分激动，最终他选择放弃读大学，直接进入勇士队球团，签约金为60万美元<ref name=BB/><ref name=mac>{{cite web | last = Rubin | first = Roger | title = Marquis Drawing Raves from Braves | publisher = ''纽约每日新闻报'' | url = http://www.nydailynews.com/archives/sports/1997/06/09/1997-06-09_marquis_drawing_raves_from_b.html | date = 1997-06-09 | accessdate = August 19, 2009}}</ref>。

== 小联盟时期 ==
{{by|1996年}}马奎斯从新人等级的[[丹维尔勇士|丹维尔勇士]]起步，这个赛季他7次登板，投出了1胜1败、防御率4.63的成绩<ref name=BB/><ref name=BC>{{cite web |title=Jason Marquis |publisher=''The Baseball Cube'' |url=http://www.thebaseballcube.com/players/M/Jason-Marquis.shtml |accessdate=July 20, 2009 |archive-date=2009-07-17 |archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20090717065717/http://www.thebaseballcube.com/players/M/Jason-Marquis.shtml |dead-url=no }}</ref>。在23局的投球中送出24次三振和7次保送<ref name=MILB>{{cite web|last=Sickels|first=John|title=Prospect Retrospective: Jason Marquis|publisher=''Minor League Ball''|url=http://www.minorleagueball.com/2005/4/29/125551/899|date=April 29, 2005|accessdate=July 20, 2009|archive-date=2016-03-03|archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20160303231623/http://www.minorleagueball.com/2005/4/29/125551/899|dead-url=no}}</ref>。

第二年马奎斯升上1A的[[罗马勇士|马孔勇士]]，他投出了14胜10败、防御率4.38的成绩，其中他的14胜追平了队史单赛季纪录。他被[[美国棒球|美国棒球]]杂志选为勇士队第五号新秀<ref name=BB/><ref name=MLB/><ref name=BC/><ref>{{cite web | url = http://www.braves400.org/event_gameboree_phil_niekro.html | title = Phil Niekro Award:  Braves Outstanding Minor League Pitcher | publisher = ''Braves400'' | accessdate = 2009-07-20 | deadurl = yes | archiveurl = https://web.archive.org/web/20110725101112/http://www.braves400.org/event_gameboree_phil_niekro.html | archivedate = 2011-07-25 }}</ref>。“他就像一个目标瞄准大联盟的球员，”球队的投手教练[[马克·罗斯|马克·罗斯]]（[[:en:Mark_Rose|Mark Rose]]）说道，“他做得非常棒。”<ref name=mac/>

{{by|1998年}}马奎斯升上高阶1A，当时他是[[卡罗莱纳联盟|卡罗莱纳联盟]]年纪最轻的投手。但他在[[丹维尔97|丹维尔97]]投得并不理想，先发22场仅仅拿到2胜，还有12场吞下败投<ref name=BB/><ref name=MLB/>。

{{by|1999年}}马奎斯继续待在1A，但换成了[[卡罗莱纳联盟|卡罗莱纳联盟]]的[[麦尔托海滩塘鹅|麦尔托海滩塘鹅]]。他开季连续20局未失分<ref name=MLB/>，被[[美国棒球|美国棒球]]评为4月15日至21日的单周最佳球员<ref>{{cite web | url = http://carolinaleague.com/league/pow/1999/pow04-22-99.html | title = Players of the Week:  4-22-99 | publisher = ''卡罗莱纳联盟'' | date = 1999-04-22 | accessdate = 2009-07-20 | archive-date = 2011-07-28 | archive-url = https://web.archive.org/web/20110728120452/http://carolinaleague.com/league/pow/1999/pow04-22-99.html | dead-url = no }}</ref>，前六场先发仅仅失掉1分的自责分。5月10日球团将他升上2A的[[格林威尔勇士|格林威尔勇士]]，并被[[美国棒球|美国棒球]]评为勇士球团的第六号新秀<ref name=MLB/><ref name=BC/>。在格林威尔期间他先发12场，投出3胜4败、防御率4.58的成绩。当年夏天马奎斯由于手肘、右肩和腹部肌肉的疼痛而不得不待在伤病名单中<ref name=BB/><ref name=MILB/>。

{{by|2000年}}马奎斯从2A起步，随後升上3A的[[里奇蒙勇士|里奇蒙勇士]]，6月份时升上了大联盟<ref name=MLB/><ref name=BC/><ref name=MILB/>。

== 大联盟生涯 ==
=== 亚特兰大勇士（2000年－03年）：进入大联盟 ===
{{MLBy|2000年}}6月，勇士队把[[约翰·洛克_(棒球运动员)|约翰·洛克]]（[[:en:John_Rocker|John Rocker]]）降入小联盟，原因是其恐吓记者<ref name=BB/>，并将马奎斯升上大联盟，当时他年仅21，是国联第十年轻的球员<ref>{{cite web | url = http://www.baseball-reference.com/leagues/NL/2000-other-leaders.shtml | title = 2000 National League Awards, All-Stars and Other Leaders | publisher = Baseball-Reference | accessdate = 2009-12-04 | archive-date = 2010-07-04 | archive-url = https://www.webcitation.org/5qxkcV3aK?url=http://www.baseball-reference.com/leagues/NL/2000-other-leaders.shtml | dead-url = no }}</ref>。6月6日在对[[多伦多蓝鸟|多伦多蓝鸟]]的比赛中，马奎斯首次在大联盟登板，但充当是中继投手的角色，接替先发的[[汤姆·葛拉文|汤姆·葛拉文]]。马奎斯在赛后说道：“这是一场晚上的比赛，我从未在灯光如此明亮的球场上打过球，就好像聚光灯都照在你身上一样。”<ref name=CT/> 7月底马奎斯被送回3A，直到9月份才再度回到大联盟。这个赛季他在大联盟登板15次，都是做为中继投手的身份出场。

{{MLBy|2001年}}马奎斯成为球队的先发投手，和[[汤姆·葛拉文|汤姆·葛拉文]]、[[葛瑞格·麦达克斯|葛瑞格·麦达克斯]]和[[凯文·米尔伍德|凯文·米尔伍德]]（[[:en:Kevin_Millwood|Kevin Millwood]]）一起组成先发轮值。该赛季由于[[九一一袭击事件|911恐怖袭击]]而中断一段时间，当年他在[[世界少棒大赛|世界少棒大赛]]的队友迈克尔·卡马拉塔（一名[[消防员|消防员]]）在这次袭击中不幸身亡。“当知道曾经在你身边的人离开这个世界的时候总是感到非常难过。”马奎斯说道<ref>{{cite web | url = http://www.nytimes.com/2001/09/21/sports/baseball-much-to-play-for-with-braves-in-town.html | last = Curry | first = Jack | title = Baseball:  Much to Play For With Braves in Town | publisher = ''纽约时报'' | date = 2001-09-21 | accessdate = 2009-08-21 | archive-date = 2016-03-04 | archive-url = https://web.archive.org/web/20160304075812/http://www.nytimes.com/2001/09/21/sports/baseball-much-to-play-for-with-braves-in-town.html | dead-url = no }}</ref>。

作为先发投手的第一个赛季，他在两出局後得点圈的被打击率仅为1成45。球团表明马奎斯是非卖品：“他将会成为一名顶级投手，我们不可能放弃他。”<ref>{{cite web | url = http://sportsillustrated.cnn.com/inside_game/tom_verducci/news/2001/06/27/verducci_insider/ | last = Verducci | first = Tom | title = New routines aid Burkett's resurgence | publisher = ''[[体育画报|体育画报]]'' | date = 2001-06-27 | accessdate = 2009-08-20 | archive-date = 2012-10-25 | archive-url = https://web.archive.org/web/20121025065941/http://sportsillustrated.cnn.com/inside_game/tom_verducci/news/2001/06/27/verducci_insider/ | dead-url = no }}</ref>{{MLBy|2002年}}马奎斯出任球队的第五号先发投手。

{{MLBy|2003年}}勇士队对先发轮值进行换血，引进了[[麦克·汉普顿|麦克·汉普顿]]（[[:en:Mike_Hampton|Mike Hampton]]）、[[拉斯·奥尔蒂斯|拉斯·奥尔蒂斯]]（[[:en:Russ_Ortiz|Russ Ortiz]]）以及[[谢恩·雷诺斯|谢恩·雷诺斯]]（[[:en:Shane_Reynolds|Shane Reynolds]]），并从2A升上[[霍拉西奥·拉米雷斯|霍拉西奥·拉米雷斯]]（[[:en:Horacio_Ramírez|Horacio Ramírez]]），因此马奎斯被移至牛棚。他对球团的决定感到很失望，便要求球队将他下放至3A，使他还能成为先发投手，并让其他球团的球探能够观察他。这个赛季他在大联盟上场21次，仅有两次作为先发出场。

赛季结束后马奎斯和[[雷·金|雷·金]]（[[:en:Ray_King|Ray King]]）、[[亚当·温赖特|亚当·温赖特]]一起被交易到[[圣路易红雀|圣路易红雀]]，换来[[J·D·德鲁|J·D·德鲁]]和[[伊莱·马雷罗|伊莱·马雷罗]]（[[:en:Eli_Marrero|Eli Marrero]]）。多年后回头看这次交易，马奎斯说：“那时我太年轻了...这件事让我感到震惊，但同时也让我明白没有什么事情是永远的。”<ref name=wag >{{cite web |last=Waggoner |first=Jim |title=Marquis looking ahead to baseball season with Colorado Rockies |publisher=''史泰登先锋报'' |url=http://www.silive.com/sports/index.ssf/2009/01/marquis_looking_ahead_to_seaso.html |date=January 29, 2009 |accessdate=August 19, 2009 |archive-date=2016-04-11 |archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20160411171901/http://www.silive.com/sports/index.ssf/2009/01/marquis_looking_ahead_to_seaso.html |dead-url=no }}</ref>

=== 圣路易红雀（2004年－06年）：世界大赛冠军、银棒奖 ===
{{MLBy|2004年}}马奎斯成为红雀队先发投手群中的一员，球队的投手教练[[戴夫·邓肯|戴夫·邓肯]]（[[:en:Dave_Duncan_(baseball)|Dave Duncan]]）称马奎斯“总能投出令人惊艳的[[伸卡球|伸卡球]]，但还需要加强。”<ref>{{cite web | url = http://mlb.mlb.com/news/article.jsp?ymd=20040417&content_id=719725&vkey=news_mlb&fext=.jsp&c_id=null | last = Wickham | first = Pete | title = Notes: Marquis a mad scientist?:  Cards pitcher sees each start as experiment | publisher = ''MLB.com'' | date = 2004-04-17 | accessdate = 2009-12-05 | archive-date = 2014-03-06 | archive-url = https://web.archive.org/web/20140306054116/http://mlb.mlb.com/news/article.jsp?ymd=20040417&content_id=719725&vkey=news_mlb&fext=.jsp&c_id=null | dead-url = no }}</ref>5月3日在对前东家[[亚特兰大勇士|亚特兰大勇士]]的比赛中，马奎斯从他的前队友[[葛瑞格·麦达克斯|葛瑞格·麦达克斯]]手上盗垒成功，而麦达克斯同样也盗垒成功<ref name=MLB/>，这是自{{MLBy|1950年}}6月11日以来首次出现双方投手在同一场比赛都盗垒成功的情形<ref name=AP>{{cite web|title="Jason Marquis"|publisher=''Athlete Promotions'' |url=http://www.athletepromotions.com/athletes/Jason-Marquis-appearance-booking-agent.php |date=|accessdate=July 20, 2009}}</ref><ref>{{cite web | url = http://www.sfgate.com/cgi-bin/article.cgi?f=/chronicle/archive/2004/05/09/SPGJ86IAMN1.DTL | last = Camps | first = Mark | title = Rare feet: Opposing hurlers steal bases in the same game | publisher = ''旧金山纪事报'' | date = 2004-05-09 | accessdate = 2009-08-20 | archive-date = 2004-09-24 | archive-url = https://web.archive.org/web/20040924235920/http://www.sfgate.com/cgi-bin/article.cgi?f=%2Fchronicle%2Farchive%2F2004%2F05%2F09%2FSPGJ86IAMN1.DTL | dead-url = no }}</ref>。5月31日至9月4日期间马奎斯拿到了11连胜，这是自{{MLBy|1985年}}[[约翰·图多尔|约翰·图多尔]]（[[:en:John_Tudor_(baseball)|John Tudor]]）以来红雀队投手的最长连胜纪录，当时图多尔也同样拿到11连胜<ref name=MLB/>。他还在8月24日至9月10日连续18⅓局未失分<ref>{{cite web | url = http://www.sportingnews.com/mlb/article/2009-07-11/braves-rockies-preview | title = Braves-Rockies Preview | publisher = ''[[体育新闻|体育新闻]]'' | date = 2009-07-11 | accessdate = 2009-07-18 }}{{Dead link|date=2018年9月 |bot=InternetArchiveBot |fix-attempted=yes }}</ref>。另外他还被红雀队球员选为[[美国职棒大联盟球员工会|大联盟球员工会]]的代表<ref>{{cite web | url = http://mlb.mlb.com/news/article.jsp?ymd=20040616&content_id=772223&vkey=news_mlb&fext=.jsp&c_id=null | last = Leach | first = Matthew | title = Notes: Cards' bench comes through | publisher = ''MLB.com'' | date = 2004-06-15 | accessdate = 2009-08-20 | archive-date = 2014-03-06 | archive-url = https://web.archive.org/web/20140306061131/http://mlb.mlb.com/news/article.jsp?ymd=20040616&content_id=772223&vkey=news_mlb&fext=.jsp&c_id=null | dead-url = no }}</ref>。

这个赛季马奎斯投出生涯迄今为止最好的15胜7败、防御率3.71的成绩，138次三振也是生涯新高，并和球队一起获得了[[国家联盟|国联]][[2004年国家联盟冠军赛|冠军]]。他的滚飞比（2.17）排名国联第二，每场先发平均用球数（104球）排名第六，胜率（.682）排名第八，胜投数（15胜）排名第九，制造双杀打数（21次）排名第十<ref name=MLB/><ref name=br>{{cite web | url = http://www.baseball-reference.com/players/m/marquja01.shtml?redir | title = Jason Marquis Statistics | publisher = ''Baseball-Reference'' | accessdate = 2009-12-05 | archive-date = 2018-09-06 | archive-url = https://web.archive.org/web/20180906195638/https://www.baseball-reference.com/players/m/marquja01.shtml?redir | dead-url = no }}</ref>，两出局后得点圈的被打击率仍然控制在很低的数字（1成63）<ref name=br/>。
