{{MLBy|2006年}}1月，马奎斯和红雀签下一年515万美元的合同，避免薪资仲裁<ref>{{cite web | url = http://mlb.mlb.com/NASApp/mlb/news/press_releases/press_release.jsp?ymd=20060117&content_id=1296605&vkey=pr_stl&fext=.jsp&c_id=stl | title = Cardinals avoid arbitration with Marquis:  Agree to terms on a one-year deal | publisher = ''MLB.com'' | date = 2006-01-17 | accessdate = 2009-08-17}}</ref>。马奎斯开季非常顺利，7月23日还成为国联第一位拿到12胜的投手<ref>{{cite web | url = http://www.sportingnews.com/yourturn/viewtopic.php?t=111029 | title = Cameron puts Padres back on top | publisher = ''体育新闻'' | date = 2006-07-23 | accessdate = 2009-08-21 }}{{dead link|date=2018年1月 |bot=InternetArchiveBot |fix-attempted=yes }}</ref>。但在下半季表现不佳，最终整季的成绩为14胜16败，防御率高达6.02，在大联盟所有投球超过162局的投手中仅低于[[西雅图水手|西雅图水手]]的[[乔尔·皮内罗|乔尔·皮内罗]]（防御率6.36）。他的失分（136）在大联盟所有投手中是最高的，败场数（16场）和被全垒打数（35支）则在国联是最高的。他还有两场极高失分的比赛，6月21日对[[芝加哥白袜|芝加哥白袜]]主投5局失13分自责分，三周后对[[亚特兰大勇士|亚特兰大勇士]]主投5局失12分<ref>{{cite web | url = http://nwitimes.com/sports/other/professional/article_0f3702b3-b7f5-5b45-86bd-81a531c5345c.html | last = Castle | first = George | title = If only Marquis could bottle success | publisher = ''NWI.com'' | date = 2008-04-05 | accessdate = 2009-08-22 | archive-date = 2012-08-29 | archive-url = https://web.archive.org/web/20120829204335/http://www.nwitimes.com/sports/other/professional/article_0f3702b3-b7f5-5b45-86bd-81a531c5345c.html | dead-url = no }}</ref>。马奎斯说：“显然这些苦果很难吞下去，作为球队的一员，我应该承担责任。”<ref>{{cite web | url = http://mlb.mlb.com/news/article.jsp?ymd=20061219&content_id=1764392&vkey=hotstove2006&fext=.jsp | last = Muskat | first = Carrie | title = Cubs finalize contract with MarquisL  Veteran right-hander's three-year deal worth $21 million | publisher = ''MLB.com'' | date = 2006-12-19 | accessdate = 2009-12-16 | archive-date = 2014-01-12 | archive-url = https://web.archive.org/web/20140112101945/http://mlb.mlb.com/news/article.jsp?ymd=20061219&content_id=1764392&vkey=hotstove2006&fext=.jsp | dead-url = no }}</ref>

马奎斯入选了该赛季季後赛红雀队的名单，但未在[[2006年国家联盟分区赛|国联分区赛]]登场。之后的[[2006年国家联盟冠军赛|国联冠军赛]]和[[2006年世界大赛|世界大赛]]他并未进入红雀队名单，红雀队最终获得了世界大赛冠军。

=== 芝加哥小熊（2007年－08年）：生涯首支满贯全垒打 ===
[[File:Marquis_at_the_plate_4_22_08cropped.jpg|300px]]
{{MLBy|2006年}}12月，马奎斯和[[芝加哥小熊|芝加哥小熊]]签下三年总价值2100万美元的合同<ref name=CJN/>。他穿上了[[萨米·索萨|萨米·索萨]]之前穿过的21号球衣（索萨的生涯第600支全垒打就是从马奎斯手中击出的）<ref name=CJN/>。

{{MLBy|2007年}}5月9日马奎斯对[[匹兹堡海盗|匹兹堡海盗]]投出了一场3安打完封胜的比赛，其中他连续解决了前16名打者，直到第六局才被海盗队[[游击手|游击手]][[唐·凯利|唐·凯利]]（[[:en:Don_Kelly_(baseball)|Don Kelly]]）击出一垒安打。这场比赛仅耗时2小时6分钟，马奎斯三振了5名打者，用球数为109。他的队友[[雅克·琼斯|雅克·琼斯]]（[[:en:Jacque_Jones|Jacque Jones]]）评价他：“他的球速很快，又极具下沉，他十分出色。”<ref>{{cite web | url = http://www.suntimes.com/sports/baseball/cubs/379533,CST-SPT-cub10.article | last = Wittenmeyer | first = Gordon | title = Marquis is magnificent:  Right-hander's three-hit shutout is Cubs' first complete game of year | work = ''芝加哥太阳时报'' | date = 2007-05-10 | accessdate = 2009-12-16 | deadurl = yes | archiveurl = https://web.archive.org/web/20071007051057/http://www.suntimes.com/sports/baseball/cubs/379533,CST-SPT-cub10.article | archivedate = 2007-10-07 }}</ref> 马奎斯认为自己的持续性是自己成功的关键：“整场比赛我的投手保持了一致性，我感觉我一次又一次在重复着投相同的球，我相信这就是我成功的地方。”<ref>{{cite web | url = http://sports.yahoo.com/mlb/recap?gid=270509116 | last = Gano | first = Rick | title = Chi Cubs 1, Pittsburgh 0 | publisher = ''雅虎'' | accessdate = 2007-06-06 | archive-date = 2016-08-27 | archive-url = https://web.archive.org/web/20160827102215/https://sports.yahoo.com/mlb/recap?gid=270509116 | dead-url = no }}</ref>

{{MLBy|2007年}}整个赛季马奎斯投出了12胜9败、防御率4.60的成绩，完封场数（1次）排名国联第二，触身球次数（13次）排名第五<ref>{{cite web | url = http://www.fangraphs.com/leaders.aspx?pos=all&stats=pit&lg=nl&qual=y&type=1&season=2007 | title = National League Leaderboards » 2007 » Pitchers » Advanced Statistics | publisher = ''FanGraphs Baseball'' | access-date = 2009-12-16 | archive-date = 2016-03-03 | archive-url = https://web.archive.org/web/20160303193006/http://www.fangraphs.com/leaders.aspx?pos=all&stats=pit&lg=nl&qual=y&type=1&season=2007 | dead-url = no }}</ref>，在比赛末段和比分接近时他的被打击率只有2成29<ref name=AP/>。

{{MLBy|2008年}}马奎斯担任小熊队的五号先发投手<ref>{{cite web | url = http://www.chicagotribune.com/sports/chi-25-cubs-chicagomar25,1,7852919.story | title = Ethics | publisher = [[芝加哥論壇報|芝加哥論壇報]] }}{{dead link|date=2018年1月 |bot=InternetArchiveBot |fix-attempted=yes }}</ref>。尽管他往年下半季的成绩都不佳，但总教练[[盧·皮涅拉|盧·皮涅拉]]还是继续让他担任先发，马奎斯也没辜负教练的期望，他在8月投出了3胜1败、防御率3.90的成绩，仅次于7月份的防御率3.81，是全年第二好的单月成绩。整个赛季他投出了11胜9败、防御率4.53的成绩，特别是两出局得点圈有人时的被打击率只有1成92<ref name=br/>。在打击方面，马奎斯职业生涯首度单季击出两支全垒打，其中9月22日从[[纽约大都会|纽约大都会]]的新秀投手[[乔恩·尼泽|乔恩·尼泽]]（[[:en:Jon_Niese|Jon Niese]]）手中击出生涯首支[[满贯全垒打|满贯全垒打]]，这是自{{MLBy|1950年}}[[底特律老虎|底特律老虎]]的[[索尔·罗戈文|索尔·罗戈文]]（[[:en:Saul_Rogovin|Saul Rogovin]]）以来首位犹太裔投手击出满贯全垒打<ref>{{cite web | url = http://www.njjewishnews.com/njjn.com/100908/sptPlentyOfHighlights.html | last = Kaplan | first = Ron | title = Plenty of highlights for Jewish Major Leaguers in ‘08 | publisher = ''新泽西犹太新闻报'' | date = 2008-10-09 | accessdate = 2009-05-22 | archive-url = https://web.archive.org/web/20110615131512/http://www.njjewishnews.com/njjn.com/100908/sptPlentyOfHighlights.html | archive-date = 2011-06-15 | dead-url = yes }}</ref>。这场比赛他打回5分打点，也创下生涯新高<ref>{{cite web | url = http://chicago.cubs.mlb.com/news/gameday_recap.jsp?ymd=20080922&content_id=3528388&vkey=recap&fext=.jsp&c_id=chc | last = Muskat | first = Carrie | title = Marquis simply grand in win over Mets | publisher = ''MLB.com,'' | date = 2008-09-23 | accessdate = 2009-08-17 | deadurl = yes | archiveurl = https://web.archive.org/web/20080926004150/http://chicago.cubs.mlb.com/news/gameday_recap.jsp?ymd=20080922&content_id=3528388&vkey=recap&fext=.jsp&c_id=chc | archivedate = 2008-09-26 }}</ref>。

这个赛季他随球队参加了季後赛，担任中继投手<ref>{{cite web | url = http://chicago.cubs.mlb.com/news/article.jsp?ymd=20080926&content_id=3554007&vkey=news_chc&fext=.jsp&c_id=chc | last = Muskat | first = Carrie | title = Piniella names Cubs starters for NLDS | publisher = ''MLB.com'' | date = 2008-09-26 | accessdate = 2009-08-17 | deadurl = yes | archiveurl = https://web.archive.org/web/20080929225044/http://chicago.cubs.mlb.com/news/article.jsp?ymd=20080926&content_id=3554007&vkey=news_chc&fext=.jsp&c_id=chc | archivedate = 2008-09-29 }}</ref>。他在[[2008年国家联盟分区赛|国联分区赛]]第一场九局上半登板投球，被[[洛杉矶道奇|洛杉矶道奇]]的[[罗素·马丁|罗素·马丁]]击出一支阳春全垒打，这也是他在这个系列赛的唯一一次上场，红雀最终也负于道奇，未能晋级<ref>{{cite web | url = http://chicago.cubs.mlb.com/news/gameday_recap.jsp?ymd=20081001&content_id=3579511&vkey=recap&fext=.jsp&c_id=chc | last = Muskat | first = Carrie | title = Dempster baffled by lack of control | publisher = ''MLB.com'' | date = 2008-10-02 | accessdate = 2009-08-17 | deadurl = yes | archiveurl = https://web.archive.org/web/20081004232824/http://chicago.cubs.mlb.com/news/gameday_recap.jsp?ymd=20081001&content_id=3579511&vkey=recap&fext=.jsp&c_id=chc | archivedate = 2008-10-04 }}</ref>。

=== 科罗拉多落矶（2009年）：全明星 ===
{{MLBy|2009年}}1月6日，马奎斯被小熊队送到[[科罗拉多落矶|科罗拉多落矶]]，交换[[路易斯·坎諾|路易斯·坎諾]]<ref>{{cite web | url = http://colorado.rockies.mlb.com/news/press_releases/press_release.jsp?ymd=20090106&content_id=3734370&vkey=pr_col&fext=.jsp&c_id=col | title = Rockies complete deal for :  Acquisition of right-hander leaves one rotation spot available | publisher = ''MLB.com'' | date = 2009-01-06 | accessdate = 2009-08-17 | deadurl = yes | archiveurl = https://web.archive.org/web/20120310084324/http://colorado.rockies.mlb.com/news/press_releases/press_release.jsp?ymd=20090106&content_id=3734370&vkey=pr_col&fext=.jsp&c_id=col | archivedate = 2012年3月10日 | df =  }}</ref>。落矶队的总经理[[丹·奥多德|丹·奥多德]]（[[:en:Dan_O'Dowd|Dan O'Dowd]]）说：“我们喜欢他的运动精神、年龄和耐久性。”<ref name=wag/>

赛季间歇期马奎斯还对他的投球姿势做了些微的改变，出手点在通过平衡点时停留时间更长，脚步也往前跨了2到3英寸，使得他能够在最高点时出手<ref>{{cite web | url = http://www.silive.com/sports/index.ssf/2009/06/minor_adjustments_yield_major.html | title = Minor adjustments yield major results for Jason Marquis | publisher = ''史泰登先锋报'' | date = 2009-06-17 | accessdate = 2009-08-19 | archive-date = 2016-03-04 | archive-url = https://web.archive.org/web/20160304050240/http://www.silive.com/sports/index.ssf/2009/06/minor_adjustments_yield_major.html | dead-url = no }}</ref><ref>{{cite web | url = http://colorado.rockies.mlb.com/news/print.jsp?ymd=20090710&content_id=5807986&vkey=news_col&fext=.jsp&c_id=col | last = Sio | first = Cheng | title = Marquis credits sinker for reemergence | publisher = ''MLB.com'' | date = 2009-07-11 | accessdate = 2009-07-18 | deadurl = yes | archiveurl = https://web.archive.org/web/20160303194402/http://colorado.rockies.mlb.com/news/print.jsp?ymd=20090710&content_id=5807986&vkey=news_col&fext=.jsp&c_id=col | archivedate = 2016年3月3日 | df =  }}</ref>。记者们认为他的改姿势取得初步的成功，增加了滚地球比率<ref>{{cite web | url = http://mlb.mlb.com/news/article.jsp?ymd=20090619&content_id=5418658&vkey=recap&fext=.jsp&c_id=mlb | last = Harding | first = Thomas | title = Marquis keeps Pirates groundedL  Rockies righty induces 20 groundouts in 8 2/3 innings | publisher = ''MLB.com'' | date = 2009-06-20 | accessdate = 2009-08-19 | archive-date = 2013-10-23 | archive-url = https://web.archive.org/web/20131023082607/http://mlb.mlb.com/news/article.jsp?ymd=20090619&content_id=5418658&vkey=recap&fext=.jsp&c_id=mlb | dead-url = no }}</ref><ref>{{cite web | url = http://mvn.com/upintherockies/2009/06/marquiss-key-to-success-more-grounders.html | last = Stephenson | first = Tom | title = Marquis's key to success: More grounders | publisher = ''MVN.com'' | date = 2009-06-20 | accessdate = 2009-08-19 | deadurl = yes | archiveurl = https://web.archive.org/web/20090627161316/http://mvn.com/upintherockies/2009/06/marquiss-key-to-success-more-grounders.html | archivedate = 2009-06-27 }}</ref>。

{{MLBy|2009年}}6月30日马奎斯投出了一场两安打无保送、17个滚地球的完投完封胜，用球数仅为86球，同时也成为国联第一个拿到10胜的投手。他封锁住了当时全联盟战绩排名第一的[[洛杉矶道奇|洛杉矶道奇]]的打线，以3比0击败对方的王牌投手[[查德·毕林斯利|查德·毕林斯利]]，其中他还打回全队3分得分中的两分<ref>{{cite web | url = http://www.google.com/hostednews/ap/article/ALeqM5i-N0FShyB-DFjiS1lIwsHoXk_-XgD995EGTO0 | title = Rockies' Jason Marquis beats Dodgers with 2-hitter | work = ''[[美联社|美联社]]'' | date = 2009-06-30 | accessdate = 2009-07-20}}</ref>。大联盟官方网站[[MLB.com|MLB.com]]认为这是“落矶队历史上投得最好的一场比赛”，[[ESPN|ESPN]]的评论员则认为马奎斯当天是“[[鲍勃·吉布森|鲍勃·吉布森]]（[[:en:Bob_Gibson|Bob Gibson]]）、[[奥勒尔·赫西瑟|奥勒尔·赫西瑟]]（[[:en:Orel_Hershiser|Orel Hershiser]]）和[[葛瑞格·麦达克斯|葛瑞格·麦达克斯]]三人的结合体”<ref>{{cite web | url = http://mlb.mlb.com/news/article.jsp?ymd=20090630&content_id=5624192&vkey=recap&fext=.jsp&c_id=mlb | last = Harding | first = Thomas | title = Marquis two-hits Dodgers for 10th win:  Rockies set club record with 21 victories in June | publisher = ''MLB.com'' | date = 2009-07-01 | accessdate = 2009-08-17 | archive-date = 2014-01-12 | archive-url = https://web.archive.org/web/20140112104000/http://mlb.mlb.com/news/article.jsp?ymd=20090630&content_id=5624192&vkey=recap&fext=.jsp&c_id=mlb | dead-url = no }}</ref><ref>{{cite web | url = http://myespn.go.com/blogs/sweetspot/0-4-2/Marquis-winning-ground-war.html | title = Marquis winning ground war | publisher = ''ESPN'' | date = 2009-07-01 | accessdate = 2009-08-19 | deadurl = yes | archiveurl = https://web.archive.org/web/20090704131340/http://myespn.go.com/blogs/sweetspot/0-4-2/Marquis-winning-ground-war.html | archivedate = 2009-07-04 }}</ref>。

7月5日马奎斯被[[费城费城人|费城费城人]]总教练[[查理·曼努埃尔|查理·曼努埃尔]]（[[:en:Charlie_Manuel|Charlie Manuel]]）选入全明星阵容，这是落矶队历史上第五位入选[[美国职棒大联盟全明星赛|全明星赛]]的投手<ref>{{cite web | url = http://colorado.rockies.mlb.com/news/article.jsp?ymd=20090705&content_id=5706696&vkey=news_col&fext=.jsp&c_id=col | last = Harding | first = Thomas | title = Hawpe, Marquis humbled by All-Star nods:  Rockies outfielder will start in place of Mets' injured Beltran | publisher = ''MLB.com'' | date = 2009-07-05 | accessdate = 2009-08-19 | deadurl = yes | archiveurl = https://web.archive.org/web/20090709201739/http://colorado.rockies.mlb.com/news/article.jsp?ymd=20090705&content_id=5706696&vkey=news_col&fext=.jsp&c_id=col | archivedate = 2009-07-09 }}</ref><ref>{{cite web | url = http://www.denverpost.com/sports/ci_12830395 | last = Paige | first = Woody | title = Paige: Halladay could make it happen | work = ''丹佛邮报'' | date = 2009-07-14 | accessdate = 2009-07-17 | archive-date = 2016-03-03 | archive-url = https://web.archive.org/web/20160303214611/http://www.denverpost.com/sports/ci_12830395 | dead-url = no }}</ref>。“我将珍惜我未来人生的每一天。”马奎斯得知入选的消息后说<ref>{{cite web | url = http://www.chicagotribune.com/sports/baseball/whitesox/chi-14-all-star-bits-jul14,0,70452.story | author = Phil Rogers和Dave van Dyck | title = Blue Jays All-Star Roy Halladay prepared to move on to another team | publisher = ''芝加哥论坛报'' | date = 2009-07-14 | accessdate = 2009-07-18 | archive-url = https://web.archive.org/web/20090717041418/http://www.chicagotribune.com/sports/baseball/whitesox/chi-14-all-star-bits-jul14,0,70452.story | archive-date = 2009-07-17 | dead-url = yes }}</ref>。他在随后的一天对[[华盛顿国民|华盛顿国民]]投出8局无失分的比赛，拿下赛季第11胜，成为队史上第三位在全明星赛之前拿到11胜以上的投手，另两位是{{MLBy|2003年}}的[[肖恩·查孔|肖恩·查孔]]（[[:en:Shawn_Chacón|Shawn Chacón]]）和{{MLBy|2008年}}的[[艾伦·库克|艾伦·库克]]（[[:en:Aaron_Cook_(baseball)|Aaron Cook]]）<ref>{{cite web | url = http://www.google.com/hostednews/ap/article/ALeqM5gCmyXbDN43eSOkmblXh1IuiwU4-QD999BPBO1 | last = Graham | first = Pat | title = Marquis wins major league-leading 11th game | work = ''美联社'' | date = 2009-07-06 | accessdate = 2009-07-20}}</ref>。

在[[2009年美国职棒大联盟全明星赛|全明星赛]]赛前介绍球员的仪式上，身为前红雀成员的马奎斯得到了除红雀队球员以外现场最大的欢呼声。第九局时他在牛棚裏热身，但未能登场<ref>{{cite web | url = http://www.silive.com/sports/index.ssf/2009/07/jason_marquis_savors_first_all.html | last = Hart | first = Stephen | title = Jason Marquis savors first All-Star Game | publisher = ''史泰登先锋报'' | date = 2009-07-15 | accessdate = 2009-07-18 | archive-date = 2016-03-04 | archive-url = https://web.archive.org/web/20160304051116/http://www.silive.com/sports/index.ssf/2009/07/jason_marquis_savors_first_all.html | dead-url = no }}</ref>。他还和一同入选全明星赛的队友[[布拉德·霍普|布拉德·霍普]]买了30根球棒和50件全明星赛T恤送给落矶队的球员、教练和球团工作人员。“我要让他们知道我们有多么感谢他们，是他们帮助我们进入了全明星赛。”马奎斯说<ref>{{cite web | url = http://www.denverpost.com/rockies/ci_12839939 | last = Renck | first = Troy E. | title = Renck: Hawpe gets ball from First Fan | work = ''丹佛邮报'' | date = 2009-07-15 | accessdate = 2009-07-18 | archive-date = 2016-03-03 | archive-url = https://web.archive.org/web/20160303220157/http://www.denverpost.com/rockies/ci_12839939 | dead-url = no }}</ref>。

这个赛季马奎斯制造了353次滚地球出局和28次双杀，均排名国联第二，55.8%的滚地球比率和3.53球的平均每打席用球量排名国联第三，15场胜投和15球的平均每局用球量则排名第四<ref name=br/><ref>{{cite web | url = http://colorado.rockies.mlb.com/stats/sortable_player_stats.jsp?teamPosCode=all&statType=2&timeFrame=1&c_id=col&section2=1&sitSplit=&venueID=&statSet2=1&subScope=teamCode&baseballScope=NL&timeSubFrame=2009&&sortByStat=W | title = National League Pitching Stats, 2009 | publisher = ''MLB.com'' | accessdate = October 9, 2009}}</ref><ref>{{cite web | url = http://www.fangraphs.com/statss.aspx?playerid=105&position=P | title = Jason Marquis | publisher = ''Fangraphs'' | accessdate = October 9, 2009 | archive-date = 2019-10-28 | archive-url = https://web.archive.org/web/20191028041426/https://www.fangraphs.com/statss.aspx?playerid=105&position=P | dead-url = no }}</ref><ref>{{cite web | url = http://espn.go.com/mlb/stats/pitching/_/seasontype/2/league/nl/sort/pitchesPerPlateAppearance/type/expanded-2/order/false/minip/160 | title = MLB Player Pitching Stats - 2009 | publisher = ''ESPN'' | accessdate = October 9, 2009 | archive-date = 2016-03-03 | archive-url = https://web.archive.org/web/20160303165826/http://espn.go.com/mlb/stats/pitching/_/seasontype/2/league/nl/sort/pitchesPerPlateAppearance/type/expanded-2/order/false/minip/160 | dead-url = no }}</ref>。他是6位2004年至09年都拿到11胜以上的投手之一<ref>{{cite web | url = http://www.nytimes.com/2009/12/05/sports/baseball/05pitcher.html | last = Shpigel | first = Ben | title = Wherever He Pitches, Staten Island’s Jason Marquis Wins | publisher = ''[[纽约时报|纽约时报]]'' | date = December 4, 2009 | accessdate = December 11, 2009 | archive-date = 2013-07-31 | archive-url = https://web.archive.org/web/20130731235530/http://www.nytimes.com/2009/12/05/sports/baseball/05pitcher.html | dead-url = no }}</ref>，另外五位是[[卡斯登·查尔斯·沙巴西亚|CC·沙巴西亚]]、[[德瑞克·洛夫|德瑞克·洛夫]]、[[尤汉·山塔纳|尤汉·山塔纳]]、[[约翰·雷基|约翰·雷基]]和[[哈维尔·巴斯克斯|哈维尔·巴斯克斯]]。在打击方面，马奎斯得到的7分在大联盟投手中排名第三，二垒安打数（3支）和打点（8分）排名第六<ref>[http://mlb.mlb.com/stats/sortable_player_stats.jsp?teamPosCode=1&statType=1&timeFrame=1&Submit=Submit&c_id=mlb&subScope=pos&sitSplit=&venueID=&baseballScope=NL&=&=&=&=&timeSubFrame=2009&&sortByStat=RBI]</ref>。

马奎斯跟随球队参加了季後赛，这是他所效力的球队连续第10个赛季进入季後赛<ref>{{cite web | url = http://www.chron.com/disp/story.mpl/life/hoffman/6633738.html | last = Hoffman | first = Ken | title = Justice is served — on a plate | publisher = ''休斯敦纪事报'' | date = September 23, 2009 | accessdate = October 9, 2009 | archive-date = 2010-01-09 | archive-url = https://web.archive.org/web/20100109032704/http://www.chron.com/disp/story.mpl/life/hoffman/6633738.html | dead-url = no }}</ref>。

赛季结束后，马奎斯成为[[自由球员|自由球员]]，落矶队提供给他仲裁<ref>{{cite web | url = http://msn.foxsports.com/mlb/story/10469648/Marquis-denies-report-that-he's-mad-at-Rockies | last = Rosenthal | first = Ken | title = Marquis denies report that he's mad at Rockies | publisher = ''福克斯新闻'' | date = December 3, 2009 | accessdate = December 4, 2009 | deadurl = yes | archiveurl = https://web.archive.org/web/20091207083546/http://msn.foxsports.com/mlb/story/10469648/Marquis-denies-report-that-he%27s-mad-at-Rockies | archivedate = 2009年12月7日 }}</ref>，但他拒绝了这份一年无保障的合同，他希望能得到一份复数年合约<ref>{{cite web | last = Harding | first = Thomas | url = http://colorado.rockies.mlb.com/news/article.jsp?ymd=20091207&content_id=7771598&vkey=news_col&fext=.jsp&c_id=col | title = Betancourt accepts arbitration from Rockies | publisher = ''[[MLB.com|MLB.com]]'' | date = December 7, 2009 | accessdate = December 8, 2009 | deadurl = yes | archiveurl = https://web.archive.org/web/20091212230056/http://colorado.rockies.mlb.com/news/article.jsp?ymd=20091207&content_id=7771598&vkey=news_col&fext=.jsp&c_id=col | archivedate = 2009年12月12日 }}</ref>。据称有包括[[纽约大都会|纽约大都会]]和[[费城费城人|费城费城人]]在内的多支球队对他有兴趣<ref>{{cite web | url = http://mlb.mlb.com/news/article.jsp?ymd=20091130&content_id=7730374&vkey=news_mlb&fext=.jsp&c_id=mlb | last = Noble | first = Marty | title = Minaya to move at own pace at Meetings | publisher = ''MLB.com'' | date = December 2, 2009 | accessdate = December 4, 2009 | archive-date = 2009-12-12 | archive-url = https://web.archive.org/web/20091212235539/http://mlb.mlb.com/news/article.jsp?ymd=20091130&content_id=7730374&vkey=news_mlb&fext=.jsp&c_id=mlb | dead-url = no }}</ref><ref>{{cite web | url = http://www.courierpostonline.com/article/20091129/SPORTS01/911290351/1002/sports/Mathieson-on-fast-track-back-to-majors | title = Mathieson on fast track back to majors | publisher = ''Cherry Hill Courier Post'' | date = November 29, 2009 | accessdate = December 4, 2009}}</ref>。

