== 球風 ==
=== 投球 ===
马奎斯是一位[[滚地球型投手|滚地球型投手]]，极度依赖他的[[伸卡球|伸卡球]]。他出手比其他绝大多数投手重，因此球的位移比较大，球多数进入[[好球带|好球带]]的下半部，造成打者击成滚地球。[[滑球|滑球]]也是他的主要应用球种。另外他的[[曲球|曲球]]和[[变速球|变速球]]也有一定水准<ref name=BB/><ref>{{cite web | url = http://sportsillustrated.cnn.com/baseball/mlb/2001/spring_training/news/2001/02/04/braves_preview/ | last = King | first = Sam | title = Atlanta Braves | publisher = ''[[運動畫刊|運動畫刊]]'' | date = 2001-02-04 | accessdate = 2009-08-20 | archive-date = 2012-10-25 | archive-url = https://web.archive.org/web/20121025065910/http://sportsillustrated.cnn.com/baseball/mlb/2001/spring_training/news/2001/02/04/braves_preview/ | dead-url = no }}</ref><ref>{{cite web | url = http://sportsillustrated.cnn.com/vault/article/magazine/MAG1023371/index.htm | last = Cannella | first = Stephen | title = Enemy Lines | publisher = ''運動畫刊'' | date = 2001-08-20 | accessdate = 2009-06-21 | archive-date = 2014-03-06 | archive-url = https://web.archive.org/web/20140306054106/http://sportsillustrated.cnn.com/vault/article/magazine/MAG1023371/index.htm | dead-url = no }}</ref>。

=== 打击和跑垒 ===
马奎斯是投手中打击较为出色的一个，有时还会被教练安排[[代打|代打]]出场。他跑垒的速度快，所以有时会上场[[代跑|代跑]]<ref>{{cite web | url = http://mlb.mlb.com/news/article.jsp?ymd=20041024&content_id=904444&vkey=ds2004news&fext=.jsp&c_id=null | last = Schlegel | first = John | title = Cardinals short hops | publisher = ''MLB.com'' | date = 2004-10-25 | accessdate = 2009-08-20 | archive-date = 2014-01-12 | archive-url = https://web.archive.org/web/20140112101918/http://mlb.mlb.com/news/article.jsp?ymd=20041024&content_id=904444&vkey=ds2004news&fext=.jsp&c_id=null | dead-url = no }}</ref>。大联盟官网的记者约翰·施莱格尔（John Schlegel）曾写道：“看看马奎斯的打击练习，你感觉看到的是一个强力左打者，你可以看到他常将球扫到全垒打墙之外。再看看他往一垒跑的速度，就像一个[[外野手|外野手]]或是一个[[线卫|线卫]]，你实在无法想像他是一个投手。”<ref>{{cite web | url = http://stlouis.cardinals.mlb.com/news/article.jsp?ymd=20041026&content_id=905866&vkey=news_stl&fext=.jsp&c_id=stl | last = Schlegel | first = John | title = Athletic Marquis ready for Game 4:  Cardinals turn to youngster in must-win situation | publisher = ''MLB.com'' | date = 2004-10-26 | accessdate = 2009-08-21 | deadurl = yes | archiveurl = https://web.archive.org/web/20100119100257/http://stlouis.cardinals.mlb.com/news/article.jsp?ymd=20041026&content_id=905866&vkey=news_stl&fext=.jsp&c_id=stl | archivedate = 2010-01-19 }}</ref>

